{
  "page": "Game of Thrones: The Mad King",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Game of Thrones: The Mad King</b></i>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-TheMadKingIsComing_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TheMadKingIsComing-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> previously known under the working title <i><b>Harrenhal</b></i>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and later <i><b>The Iron Throne</b></i>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> is an upcoming <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Broadway_theatre\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Broadway theatre\">Broadway play</a> written by Duncan MacMillan.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Plot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Plot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Dramatis_personae\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Dramatis personae</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Production_history\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Production history</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Plot\">Plot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Game_of_Thrones:_The_Mad_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Plot\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The plot centers around the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Harrenhal\" title=\"Tourney at Harrenhal\">tourney at Harrenhal</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">year of the false spring</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-WiC_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-WiC-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Dramatis_personae\">Dramatis personae</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Game_of_Thrones:_The_Mad_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Dramatis personae\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ontheroad-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ontheroad-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark\" title=\"Lyanna Stark\">Lyanna Stark</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ontheroad-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ontheroad-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Howland_Reed\" title=\"Howland Reed\">Howland Reed</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ontheroad-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Production_history\">Production history</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Game_of_Thrones:_The_Mad_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Production history\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The development of the play was first reported in March 2021. Developed by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>, written by Duncan MacMillan, produced by Simon Painter, Tim Lawson, Vince Gerardis, and Jonathan Sanford, and directed by Dominic Cooke, it was originally expected to make its debut in 2023.<sup id=\"cite_ref-WiC_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-WiC-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> It was delayed to late 2024,<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> and then to 2025.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ontheroad-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> In February 2026 it was announced that tickets would go on sale in April.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TheMadKingIsComing_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TheMadKingIsComing-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Game_of_Thrones:_The_Mad_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-TheMadKingIsComing-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-TheMadKingIsComing_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-TheMadKingIsComing_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">George R.R. Martin (February 19, 2026) <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2026/02/19/the-mad-king-is-coming/\">The Mad King Is Coming</a>. Not A Blog. Retrieved February 20, 2026.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https://startlinginc.com/en/\">https://startlinginc.com/en/</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external free\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2023/07/22/actors-join-the-strike/\">https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2023/07/22/actors-join-the-strike/</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-WiC-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-WiC_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-WiC_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https://winteriscoming.net/2021/03/30/game-thrones-broadway-play-coming-tourney-harrenhal/\">https://winteriscoming.net/2021/03/30/game-thrones-broadway-play-coming-tourney-harrenhal/</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ontheroad-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-1\">5.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-2\">5.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-3\">5.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-4\">5.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ontheroad_5-5\">5.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">George R.R. Martin (July 9, 2024) <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2024/07/09/on-the-road-again-5/\">On the Road Again</a>. Not A Blog. Retrieved June 10, 2024.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">George R.R. Martin (December 6, 2023) <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2023/12/06/a-visit-to-old-blighty/\">A Visit to Old Blighty</a>. Not A Blog. Retrieved December 7, 2023.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:ASOIAF\" title=\"Template:ASOIAF\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template_talk:ASOIAF\" title=\"Template talk:ASOIAF\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:ASOIAF&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Derived_works\" title=\"Derived works\">Derived works</a> from the world of <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Games</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li>Collectible card game: <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones_(card_game)\" title=\"A Game of Thrones (card game)\">A Game of Thrones</a></i></li>\n<li>Board g